		{
			"name":"Countermeasures",
			"type":"feature",
			"img":"icons/svg/cancel.svg",
			"system":{
				"description":{
					"value":"<ul><li><b>Identify:</b> Arcana DC 24:The crystal is an idol of Fire Lord Imix, a powerful primordial.</li><li><b>Identify:</b> Arcana (trained only) DC 33:The crystal has the power to capture creatures inside it and burn them to a crisp.</li><li><b>Identify:</b> Perception DC 17:The character sees that the crystal is rooted to the floor and immobile.</li><li><b>Identify:</b> Perception DC 24:The character notices that the crystal is hollow and emanates ripples of heat.</li><li><b>Escape:</b> Endurance DC 24 (standard action). Success: The trapped creature escapes the idol. Failure (by 5 or more): The trapped creature takes 15 fire damage.</li><li><b>Escape:</b> Endurance DC 33 (minor action). Success: The trapped creature escapes the idol. Failure (by 5 or more): The trapped creature takes 15 fire damage.</li><li><b>Free a Prisoner:</b> Arcana (trained only) DC 24 (standard action). <i>Requirement</i>: The character must be adjacent to the idol. Success: The character touches the idol and commands it to release the trapped creature. Failure (by 5 or more): The character and the trapped creature each take 15 fire damage.</li><li><b>Free a Prisoner:</b> Arcana (trained only) DC 33 (minor action). <i>Requirement</i>: The character must be adjacent to the idol. Success: The character touches the idol and commands it to release the trapped creature. Failure (by 5 or more): The character and the trapped creature each take 15 fire damage.</li><li><b>Shatter Idol:</b> If the idol drops to 0 hit points, any creature trapped within is released.</li></ul>",
